dashboard.welcomefirst: Motum-Quod * is an evidence management system to help digitize on-site and off-site processes.
dashboard.welcomesecond: Evidences of different types, always starting from one identification of who or what person. Such evidence is kept as records of a secure database and / or documents generated on-site that collect the participant's signature.
dashboard.welcomethird: Therefore, as a facilitator of electronic signature processes, it can be used in multiple environments and to resolve multiple use cases. For example, visit or attendance sheets for events or courses, commercial or labor contracts, instances in proceedings of the AAPP, etc.
